<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Bella Bouquet Shop</title>

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif ;
    background:#ffc4dc;
}

/* HEADER */
header{
    background:#ff6fa5;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
}

header img{
    width:50px;
    margin-right:10px;
}

/* NAVIGATION */
nav{
    background:white;
    padding:10px;
}

nav a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:black;
    font-weight:bold;
    margin-right:20px;
}

/* LAYOUT */
.container{
    display:flex;
}

/* MAIN CONTENT */
main{
    flex:3;
    padding:20px;
}

/* SIDEBAR */
aside{
    flex:1;
    background:#ffe0ec;
    padding:20px;
}

/* PRODUK */
.produk{
    display:flex;
    gap:20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:10px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 0 5px black;
    text-align:center;
}

.card{
    width:180px;
}

.card img{
    width:150px;
    height:150px;
    object-fit:cover;
    border-radius:10px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
    background:#ff6fa5;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:10px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<img src="logo.jpg" alt="Logo Bouquet">
<h1>Bella Bouquet Shop</h1>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Produk</a>
<a href="#">Pesanan</a>
<a href="#">Kontak</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

<main>

<section>
<h2>Hi Gais, Selamat Datang di Bella Bouquet</h2>
<p> Kami menyediakan berbagai buket cantik untuk wisuda, ulang tahun, dan hadiah spesial.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Produk Bouquet</h2>

<div class="produk">

<div class="card">
<img src="bunga.jpg" alt="Flower Bouquet">
<h3>Flower Bouquet</h3>
<p>Rp80.000</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="snack.jpg" alt="Snack Bouquet">
<h3>Snack Bouquet</h3>
<p>Rp75.000</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="Money.jpg" alt="Money Bouquet">
<h3>Money Bouquet</h3>
<p>Rp95.000(jasa only)</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="boneka.jpg" alt="Doll Bouquet">
<h3>Doll Bouquet Bouquet</h3>
<p>Rp100.000</p>
</div>


</div>

</section>

</main>

<aside>

<h3>Statistik Toko</h3>

<p>🌸 Total Produk : 4</p>
<p>🛒 Pesanan Hari Ini : 20</p>
<p>👩‍💻 Pelanggan : 500</p>

</aside>

</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Bella Bouquet Shop | Sistem Pemesanan Bouquet</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

